This is ThinkHDAPS, a disk protection monitor.

Dependencies: Python, PyGTK, gnome-python, librsvg
Please find the packages specific to your distro and install them.

To install, run:
  $ ./configure
  $ make
and as root:
  $ make install

See INSTALL for details.
